PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Cat NFT Creator
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: A Cat NFT is a unique digital collectible featuring a one-of-a-kind cat image. Each NFT is minted on the blockchain, ensuring its authenticity and ownership.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How do I create my own Cat NFT using your GUI?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our user-friendly GUI makes it easy! Simply choose your cat's features, colors, and accessories, then click 'Generate'. Once you're happy with the result, you can mint your Cat NFT directly from the app.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I sell the Cat NFTs I create?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! Once you've minted your Cat NFT, you own it and can sell it on various NFT marketplaces. Our app even integrates with popular platforms to make listing your creation quick and easy.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Are there any fees for using the Cat NFT Creator?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Creating and customizing your cat image is free. There's a small fee for minting your NFT to cover blockchain transaction costs. Check our pricing page for current rates and any special offers.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about creating your purr-fect Cat NFTs
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: A Cat NFT is a unique digital collectible of a cat image that you create and own on the blockchain. Each Cat NFT is one-of-a-kind and can be bought, sold, or traded.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How do I create a Cat NFT using this app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Simply use our intuitive GUI to customize your cat's appearance, including fur color, eye shape, accessories, and more. Once satisfied, click 'Mint' to create your unique Cat NFT on the blockchain.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Do I need cryptocurrency to create Cat NFTs?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, you'll need some cryptocurrency (usually Ethereum) to pay for the 'gas fees' associated with minting your Cat NFT on the blockchain. Make sure your wallet is connected and funded before minting.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I sell my Cat NFTs?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Once minted, your Cat NFT can be listed on various NFT marketplaces. You can set your own price and earn royalties from future sales of your unique feline creation.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Are there any limits to how many Cat NFTs I can create?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: There's no limit to the number of Cat NFTs you can create. However, remember that each minting process requires a separate transaction and associated fees. Create responsibly and consider the uniqueness of each Cat NFT.
